ype":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"f3d253c32f841c2ee5a8200601fe91f8","url_token":"jiao-wo-biao-ge-10","name":"叫我彪哥","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3c4332837f8e2d5096345f1b5d3bd9ef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3c4332837f8e2d5096345f1b5d3bd9ef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/f3d253c32f841c2ee5a8200601fe91f8","user_type":"people","headline":"OI 蒟蒻","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563319902","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546224889,"updated_time":1546224933,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e新的一年要开始了，广大网友朋友最期待的除了六老师的电影，就是您的证明了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实，我个人觉得这个提问本身就成功了！引发了一个热点，正如其它回答中提到的，您的这一事件完全可以作为一项大规模的社会调研。从中，大家都能获利！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，我还是希望您能证明出来的！难道高中生的身份和数学证明之间有什么必然的关系吗？为什么就肯定了提问者不能证明？当然，如果证明里的确存在一些错误，也希望您能虚心接受，(这是和民科的区别)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e加油！如果真的完美证明了哥德巴赫猜想，保送肯定不成问题。教授院士也是有可能的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c58b15330e56cbc74af4e7df41cb4e65_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"176\" data-rawheight=\"124\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"176\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='176'%20height='124'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"176\" data-rawheight=\"124\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"176\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c58b15330e56cbc74af4e7df41cb4e65_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":5594332