的高数老师跟我们说过，你们数学学的怎么样，我看你们严不严瑾就知道了，我看到了你老师的评论，你希望在数学上有所建树，渴求更大的舞台，但是世界上有太多太多的民科，请求你不要成为这样投机取巧的人，你要确定自己走的道路，投身于数学是很让人钦佩的一件事，如果证明没有成功，请你换个帐号，好好学习，在另一个地方发光发热，不要理会这些网络暴力，如果证明成功了，我妹妹教科书上就有你的名字了(๑\u0026gt; \u0026lt;๑），我也会在今年考研试卷上看到你。加油。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560831650,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0126363465cc73c917275fb11ff05575","url_token":"zhan-sheng-hu","name":"Louvre","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0126363465cc73c917275fb11ff05575","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560831650","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545891769,"updated_time":1545891769,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e大二学渣，觉得大学理论教授已经是很高深莫测啦，陈景润的故事大家小时候都听过，我觉没有学问本身就很高的人引导，考自己研究短短几个月内没法证明吧？这是社会研究？？？（说炒热度的人我也是醉了，答主炒热度图啥？......）\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch1\u003e这个世界上所有的人，并不是个个都有过你拥有的那些优越条件。”\u003c/h1\u003e\u003cp\u003e大家换位思考一下，如果你的言论是评论你的突发其想你会怎么看？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=2100\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=2060\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
